{
  "stem": "20035.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is the very, very, very few conversation between the two brothers, my brother and I, is we said to each other that we must survive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Because we are the men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we have to take care of mom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that dad is gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Grandpa-- is naturally gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew that she's alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That gave us the strength to fight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That job came to the end in Auschwitz, sometimes in August.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Suddenly we were-- by the way, that I would like to, just for the record, to see that once you lived in Birkenau or Auschwitz, it didn't mean if you are in camp that you are alive and you are going to survive.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It could happen during the day or at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If not enough transport came in, that mean not enough new people came in and there was room in the gas chambers and crematoriums, automatically a truck or two came in, loaded up people, took us away, took people away.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We learned that immediately, that that was a death sentence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anytime during the day, or at night, or after appel, suddenly, a truck pulled up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the truck was basically full of SS, surrounded, x people, march.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was their death, marched straight to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There is no reaction.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is-- it's-- it's-- you became not only a number, but not-normal human being who just strived for one thing, is waking up tomorrow morning, of-- of-- of-- of being alive and being to survive and waiting for the-- for the miracle to happen.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
